<br>
Remember we are already doing an unfair comparison.<br>
<br>
Melees need heals to do damage.  Casters need mana to do damage.<br>
<br>
Problem is that melees with a healer (cleric or druid) or compared against a caster with no mind buffs.  Just not a fair comparison to begin with.<br>
<br>
Best thing you can do is find a good guild and group with them.  Its amazing how many people in my guild said they like wizzees.  <br>
<br>
Also, just learn how to play your class.  Know how to avoid stealing aggro from tank (unless absolutely necessary).  Have an evac loaded and use when needed.  Root adds when chanter is not around to mez.  Show people you can play your class well, and you will get invited over and over again.<br>
<br>
If groups in your zone just wont invite you, find another zone.  Let those who didnt want to invite you to their group, struggle to find a port or transloc when they are done hunting.<br>
<br>
