<br>
For some, they think balancing needs to be done to make the game fun.  Some want to be balanced they think the current state of the game is unfair.<br>
<br>
There are good reasons to keep casters balanced.  For some specific discussion about wizard balance in particular, read the sticky threads in the &quot;Class Balance and Bugs&quot; section. <p><center>
